channel.title: Config vars
channel.description:
It's worth a shot asking here...
Just wondering if anyone has some or all of the config vars for the 317 client. If you do, it'd be appreciated. Config vars are also known as client side settings / packet 36.
If it resorts to it I'll have to do dumping and experimentation and we all know how fun that is.
Thanks!
